{"tid":1574112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"魯比奧對美國國會通過香港人權與民主法案感樂觀","createTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T12:45:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b822693a60697d7d51e3a6a4dbe3d37bf5a4e622","tid":1574112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"提出在美國國會審議《香港人權與民主法案》的共和黨參議員魯比奧表示，他對國會通過法案感到樂觀，認為法案將獲總統特朗普簽署生效。魯比奧接受美國《大西洋》雜誌訪問時指出，相信美國國會將輕易通過《香港人權與民主法案》；他說，曾與特朗普私下討論法案，認為對方對通過法案沒有表現抗拒，白宮亦表明會簽署法案。<br />\n<br />\n他不認為，特朗普會因為中美恢復貿易談判，而運用否決權去否決法案，指他向特朗普提出，中方既然正準備違反1984年與英國簽定的《中英聯合聲明》，美方如何能夠相信中方在貿易問題上會信守承諾。<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧又表示，《香港人權與民主法案》一旦通過，最重要是如何執行，包括每年檢視香港的人權與民主狀況，以及向施行鎮壓的警員等個人實施制裁，否則作用不大。"},{"pid":"49c3071543688969c2f0b45f6714cc21329326b4","tid":1574112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172364&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1172364%26csid%3D261_341&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=628010f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172364&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"edb8f52df6c37e4d5577c6f7bb5cef9de2221558","tid":1574112,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316ec181f03bc91584d733a4428775500bd4189d","tid":1574112,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"最緊要燒山收聲"},{"pid":"0c15f994a62c1d42a2cec652bede0716e31136c1","tid":1574112,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2